  "instructions": [
    "Drain tofu and cut into 2cm cubes, pat dry with paper towels",
    "Heat canola oil in large skillet or wok over medium-high heat",
    "Add tofu cubes and pan-fry 6-8 minutes until golden on all sides",
    "Remove tofu and set aside",
    "Add minced garlic and ginger to same pan, stir-fry 30 seconds",
    "Add kimchi and frozen edamame, stir-fry 3-4 minutes",
    "In small bowl, mix gochujang with soy sauce and 2 tbsp water",
    "Return tofu to pan, add gochujang mixture and toss to coat",
    "Cook 2 more minutes until heated through",
    "Drizzle with sesame oil before serving over rice"
